---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section
  id="home"
  class="min-h-[75vh] flex flex-col justify-center items-start py-12 md:py-0"
>
  <div class="w-full">
    <p class="text-[#00f2ff] font-mono mb-4 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-widest">
      // HELLO THERE, I AM
    </p>
    <h1
      class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-[5rem] font-extrabold font-display leading-[1.1] md:leading-[0.9] tracking-tight mb-6 break-words"
    >
      OSCAR<br />
      <span class="text-[#8892b0]">ARCE</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="hidden sm:block h-[1px] w-12 bg-[#a855f7]"></div>
      <p
        class="text-[#a855f7] font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs md:text-sm"
      >
        Web & Software Developer
      </p>
    </div>

    <br />
    <p
      class="text-[#8892b0] text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl font-sans leading-relaxed mb-10 md:mb-12"
    >
      Construyendo aplicaciones empresariales robustas y experiencias digitales
      cautivadoras. Especializado en arquitecturas escalables con <strong
        >.NET 8</strong
      >, interfaces interactivas con <strong>React & Astro</strong>, y
      automatización con <strong>Python</strong>.
    </p>
    <br />

    <a
      href="#projects"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 md:px-8 md:py-4 bg-[#ccd6f6] text-[#0b0d17] text-sm md:text-base font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-[#00f2ff] transition-colors duration-300 font-display w-full sm:w-auto justify-center"
    >
      EXPLORE PROJECTS
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="20"
        height="20"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        ><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline
          points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg
      >
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
